Like Baka, I know my class inside and out.  I've learned that by dealing with armor and spells I can acquire without cheating.  Rest assured you aren't likely to die based on me making some stupid mistake because I don't know my own limits.  Go ahead and hire your instant 65 cleric with Armor of Dubiousness, though, let them kill you.  You can just buy better items to make yourself look better than you are. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=4286.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=4286.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=4286.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=4286.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=4286.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=4286.topic&start=121&stop=138>7</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=4286.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=4286.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4286.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.threadControl?topicID=4286.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Comman